    <data key="d0">Automating Creative Ad Workflows for Advance Local</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1SwHH7qQ6Pc</data>
    <data key="d2">Automated pipeline converting Salesforce data into creative assets. Replaced legacy integrations with a unified serverless API, saving admin overhead and streamlining creative designer flows.</data>
